    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1892-11-05T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1892-11-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="540"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d540">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Foster</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Herbert</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1892-11-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 5, 1892</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to acknowledge the receipt of
                    your note of the 2d instant, in relation to the resignation of Baron Senfft, as
                    president of the municipal council of Apia.</p>
                <p>In view of the information which I communicated to you in our interview last
                    Thursday, this Government anticipates that Earl Rosebery will take this subject
                    again into consideration.</p>
                <p>I have, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">John W. Foster.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
